                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "my sad critique of the manifesto and the space in general is that nothing will get built, let alone maintained, that can actually be used for something real that people outside the creator or a small community of enthusiasts for a short period of time can use.\n\nIn 10 years someone will share a screenshot of a lost prototype that only worked for the demo and talk about how people in the past where doing all this amazing things and ask why worse is better won again."
